import React from 'react';

const Spinner = () => (
  <svg
    className='spinner'
    width='65px'
    height='65px'
    viewBox='0 0 66 66'
    xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
  >
    <circle
      className='path'
      fill='none'
      strokeWidth='6'
      strokeLinecap='round'
      cx='33'
      cy='33'
      r='30'
    ></circle>
  </svg>
);

export default Spinner;
